719030f-a.text:
Colonial Park: An elongated area north from West 145th Street (foreground) between Bradhurst (right) and Edgecombe (left) Aves. This set of 2 views shows a continuous perspective northward of the southern
extremity.
September 1, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.

719032f-b.text:
Colonial Park: A northward view from the southern extremity (West 145th Street), showing buildings that line the east side of Bradhurst Ave. This is a set of three views; No. 3 of which is limited.
Views 1 & 2:-September 1, 1935.
View 3:eAugust 29, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
